# --- Railway demo deploy (party-line-dev): intentionally NOT ignored ---
# railway.json / railway-entrypoint.sh / railway-seed.py are local-only and
# must never be committed to the upstream PR branch - but they must NOT be
# gitignored either: `railway up` only uploads files that aren't gitignored,
# so ignoring them would stop them deploying. Leave them untracked.